channel.title: Replacing quest tab with low detail music tab?
channel.description:
Hey, how do I replace my quest tab with the "Low Detail Quest Tab" Because you know if your in low detail then instead of a list of songs it has like word telling you that you need high detail? Well I want to replace my quest tab with that so that I can type stuff in it like the commands and such...
Or if it isn't possible I'll just remove it... How do I do that?
